pygame Primer
The 1up shroom versus green mario

The arow keys and WASD move the 1 up shroom (the protagonist).
A click (or a click and hold) will fire (a) fireball(s).

Green Mari0 is sensitive to the fireballs.
He has 33 health (1 ball takes 1 health)
Green Mario will not hesitate to go boom if prompted with 33 fireballs.

**Secret Easter Egg** The 'k' key auto-kills luigi
The 'q' key closes out the window

RUN: >> python3 game
